{"tid":2331210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭斯夫婦公開接種輝瑞新冠病毒疫苗冀加強民眾信心","createTime":"2020-12-18T15:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T15:58:04.000Z","uid":212249,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dec1c3d758b2d1cfdc6f8c7c11879ebbc5215f5a","tid":2331210,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國副總統彭斯及夫人公開接種輝瑞有份研發的新冠病毒疫苗，說希望這樣做能加強民眾對疫苗的信心；他又說美國將在短時間內批准第二款新冠病毒疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯當地周五早上，在嘉賓及傳媒見證下，接種輝瑞及BioNTech研發的新冠病毒疫苗，與彭斯同時接種的還有他的太太卡倫及美國醫務總監亞當斯。彭斯發表講話，說希望自己公開接種疫苗可以加強民眾信心。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯：「專家告訴我，疫苗由研發、生產到分發平均需要8至12年時間，現時美國能向民眾分發數以百萬計的疫苗的工作，在不足一年內完成，這的確是醫學奇蹟。卡倫及我希望今天的行動，能為美國民眾帶來信心及安慰。」<br />\n<br />\n彭斯又預告，美國將在短時間內使用第二款新冠病毒疫苗。美國總統特朗普較早時在社交網站表示，莫德納的新冠病毒疫苗已獲批准使用，但美國食品及藥物管理局未有相關公布。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯是美國批准使用輝瑞新冠病毒疫苗至今接種的最高級美國官員，但特朗普至今仍未表明會否或何時接種疫苗。有公共衞生專家認為，特朗普不願公開接種疫苗將無助建立公眾對新冠疫苗的信心。<br />\n<br />\n抗疫專家福奇亦認為，雖然特朗普曾感染新冠病毒，體內會有抗體，但不知抗體維持多久，建議特朗普接種。至於候任總統拜登，他的過渡團隊成員表示，拜登將在下星期接種新冠病毒疫苗。"},{"pid":"e20c18635aa637fd63318074166397c0c37b6b84","tid":2331210,"uid":212249,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:06:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=417146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417146&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=65d6a2e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417146&h=37390584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=417146</a>"},{"pid":"1986d0294ea97f33516dd8a542ee2f2d3569e49f","tid":2331210,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:13:35.000Z","msg":"候任監犯拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca24a3edf228f386ff8371bd14d3d85e773e95d1","tid":2331210,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:16:04.000Z","msg":"拜登個心肯撚定第一時間想打<br />\n條友平時塞係個地下室就知怕死到"},{"pid":"c96aa1babb87a8d3dee57e0695c21a6c85df35ca","tid":2331210,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"幫疫苗賣廣告 ...."},{"pid":"05ddce61ec16d9142d1005b5b6ba461f1034e498","tid":2331210,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"佢直播打針都8萬人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ca64187af2e33b1bcbd27802b7f9ef6dee9b7a","tid":2331210,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:39:05.000Z","msg":"他的過渡團隊成員表示，拜登將在下星期接種新冠病毒疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n老母麵最後一擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f5a67a38c769fd9e3ed82073ba00bdca53f857","tid":2331210,"uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"彭斯總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee21714fa66469594bd6ffcd4fd2e9bf85eea3e9","tid":2331210,"uid":47208,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"05ddce61ec16d9142d1005b5b6ba461f1034e498","tid":2331210,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"佢直播打針都8萬人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"拜登&rsquo;當選&lsquo; 有一千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2d55bbb4c9bafb0055aad2b495badcd1fdb983","tid":2331210,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee21714fa66469594bd6ffcd4fd2e9bf85eea3e9","tid":2331210,"uid":47208,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sco